column3: Oct 9 Blackrock has set up a direct lending platform in Europe with the appointment of managing director Stephan Caron.

column2: Cisco to set up $80 mln China cloud JV with TCL BEIJING
column3: Oct 9 Cisco Systems Inc will establish an $80 million joint venture with Chinese hardware manufacturer TCL Corp to invest in commercial cloud computing services
column4: TCL said in a stock exchange filing on Thursday.

column2: INSIGHT-Morgan Stanley uses client cash to chase private equity profits Oct 9 Morgan Stanley is embracing the financial reforms intended to curb its animal spirits to generate bigger profits.
CFTC sues Chicago broker for trade violations
column4: Oct 9 The compliance officer of a futures brokerage that was a top player in a market on the Chicago Board of Trade floor never reviewed company policies on floor operations or oversaw activities related to the trading floor
column5: U.S. regulators said on Thursday in a lawsuit charging the firm with violations.
